\c 1
\s Ukufika kukaJesu Kristu kuyamenyezelwa nguJohane uMbhabhathizi
\p
\v 1 Ukuqala kwevangeli likaJesu Kristu, iNdodana kaNkulunkulu\x + Mat. 14.33.\x*;
\v 2 njengokulotshiweyo kubaprofethi\x + Mat. 3.1-11. Luka 3.2-16.\x* \add ukuthi\add*: Khangela, mina ngiyathuma isithunywa sami phambi kobuso bakho, esizalungisa indlela yakho phambi kwakho\x + Mal. 3.1. Mat. 11.10. Luka 7.27.\x*.
\v 3 Ilizwi lomemezayo enkangala, \add lithi\add*: Lungisani indlela yeNkosi; qondisani izindledlana zayo\x + Isa. 40.3. Joha. 1.23.\x*.
\v 4 Kweza uJohane ebhabhathiza enkangala, etshumayela ubhabhathizo lokuphenduka kukho ukuthethelelwa kwezono\x + Mat. 26.28. Luka 1.77.\x*,
\v 5 njalo kwaphumela kuye ilizwe lonke leJudiya, labo abeJerusalema, basebebhabhathizwa bonke nguye emfuleni iJordani, bevuma izono zabo.
\v 6 Futhi uJohane wayembethe uboya bekamela, elozwezwe lwesikhumba ekhalweni lwakhe, wayesidla intethe loluju lweganga.
\p
\v 7 Watshumayela, esithi: Olamandla kulami uyeza emva kwami, engingafanele ukukhothama ngithukulule umchilo wamanyathela akhe\x + Gen. 14.23. Isa. 5.27. Luka 3.16. Joha. 1.27.\x*.
\v 8 Mina isibili ngilibhabhathize ngamanzi; kodwa yena uzalibhabhathiza ngoMoya oNgcwele.
\s Ukubhabhathizwa kukaJesu
\p
\v 9 Kwasekusithi ngalezonsuku\x + Mat. 3.13-17. Luka 3.21,22.\x* kwafika uJesu evela eNazaretha yeGalili\x + Mat. 2.23.\x*, wabhabhathizwa nguJohane eJordani.
\v 10 Wenela ukukhuphuka emanzini, wabona amazulu eqhekezeka, loMoya kungathi lijuba esehlela phezu kwakhe;
\v 11 kwasekusiza ilizwi livela emazulwini, \add lathi\add*: Wena uyiNdodana yami ethandekayo, engithokoza ngayo.
\s Ukulingwa kukaJesu
\p
\v 12 Njalo uMoya\x + 1.12,13, Mat. 4.1-11. Luka 4.1-13.\x* wahle wamqhubela enkangala\x + Mat. 9.38. Joha. 10.4.\x*.
\v 13 Wayekhona-ke lapho enkangala insuku ezingamatshumi amane elingwa nguSathane, wayelezilo, ingilosi zasezimnceda.
\s UJesu uqala ukutshumayela
\p
\v 14 Kwathi emva kokunikelwa kukaJohane\x + Mat. 4.12.\x*, uJesu wafika eGalili, etshumayela ivangeli lombuso kaNkulunkulu\x + Mat. 4.23.\x*,
\v 15 njalo esithi: Isikhathi sigcwalisekile\x + Dan. 9.25. Gal. 4.4. Efe. 1.10. Heb. 1.2.\x*, njalo umbuso kaNkulunkulu ususondele; phendukani, likholwe ivangeli\x + Mat. 4.17. Mat. 3.2.\x*.
\s Ukubizwa kwabafundi bakuqala
\p
\v 16 Kwathi ehambahamba elwandle lweGalili wabona uSimoni loAndreya umfowabo, bephosela imbule olwandle; ngoba babengabagoli benhlanzi\x + Mat. 4.18-22. Luka 5.2-11. Joha. 1.40-42.\x*.
\v 17 UJesu wasesithi kubo: Ngilandelani, ngizalenza libe ngabagoli babantu.
\v 18 Njalo bahle batshiya amambule abo, bamlandela.
\v 19 Eseqhubeke ibangana esuka lapho, wabona uJakobe okaZebediya, loJohane umfowabo, labo babesemkhunjini belungisa amambule \add abo\add*.
\v 20 Njalo wahle wababiza; basebetshiya uyise uZebediya emkhunjini leziqhatshwa, basuka bamlandela.
\s Ukusiliswa kwezigulane eKapenawume
\p
\v 21 Basebengena eKapenawume\x + Mat. 4.13. Luka 4.31-37.\x*; kwathi ngesabatha wahle wangena esinagogeni, wafundisa\x + 1.39. Mat. 4.23.\x*.
\v 22 Basebebabaza ngemfundiso yakhe\x + Mat. 7.28,29.\x*; ngoba wabafundisa njengolamandla, njalo kungenjengababhali\x + Mat. 7.28,29.\x*.
\p
\v 23 Futhi kwakukhona esinagogeni labo umuntu owayelomoya ongcolileyo, wasememeza,
\v 24 wathi: Yekela, silani lawe, Jesu weNazaretha? Uze ukusibhubhisa yini\x + Mat. 8.29. 2 Sam. 16.10.\x*? Ngiyakwazi wena ukuthi ungubani\x + Mat. 25.24.\x*: ONgcwele kaNkulunkulu\x + Dan. 9.24. Seb. 3.14. Luka 1.35. 1 Joha. 2.20. Hlab. 16.10. Seb. 2.27; 13.35.\x*.
\v 25 UJesu wasemkhuza\x + Mat. 12.16.\x*, wathi\x + 1.34. Mat. 8.4.\x*: Thula, uphume kuye\x + Mat. 22.12.\x*.
\v 26 Futhi umoya ongcolileyo emhlukuluza ekhala ngelizwi elikhulu, waphuma kuye\x + 9.20,26. Luka 9.39.\x*.
\v 27 Basebemangala bonke, baze babuzana, bathi: Kuyini lokhu? Yimfundiso bani entsha le, ukuthi ngamandla uyalaya labomoya abangcolileyo, futhi bamlalele.
\v 28 Njalo yahle yaphuma indumela yakhe esigabeni sonke seGalili esizingelezeleyo.
\s Uninazala kaPetro labanye abagulayo bayasiliswa
\p
\v 29 Njalo bahle baphuma\x + Mat. 8.14-16. Luka 4.38-41.\x* esinagogeni, bangena endlini kaSimoni loAndreya, kanye loJakobe loJohane\x + 1.21,23. 3.1.\x*.
\v 30 Futhi uninazala kaSimoni wayelele eloqhuqho, njalo bahle bamtshela ngaye\x + Mat. 13.20.\x*;
\v 31 wasesondela, wabamba isandla sakhe wamvusa; futhi uqhuqho lwahle lwamyekela, wabasebenzela.
\p
\v 32 Kwathi sekuhlwile, ilanga selitshona, baletha kuye bonke abagulayo lababengenwe ngamadimoni\x + Luka 4.40.\x*;
\v 33 njalo umuzi wonke wawubuthene emnyango\x + 1.21.\x*.
\v 34 Wasesilisa abanengi ababegula izifo ezitshiyeneyo, wakhupha amadimoni amanengi\x + Mat. 4.23.\x*, kodwa kavumelanga amadimoni ukuthi akhulume\x + 3.11,12. Seb. 16.17,18.\x*, ngoba ayemazi.
\s UJesu uyakhuleka; uyasuka eKapenawume
\p
\v 35 Njalo ekuseni kusesemnyama kakhulu wavuka waphuma\x + Luka 4.42-44.\x*, waya endaweni eyinkangala\x + Mat. 14.23.\x*, wakhuleka khona\x + Mat. 14.23.\x*.
\v 36 USimoni lababelaye basebemdingisisa;
\v 37 sebemtholile bathi kuye: Bonke bayakudinga.
\v 38 Wasesithi kubo: Asiye emizini eseduze, ukuze ngitshumayele lakhona; ngoba ngiphumele lokhu\x + Isa. 61.1.\x*.
\v 39 Wasetshumayela emasinagogeni abo kulo lonke eleGalili, ekhupha amadimoni\x + 1.21. Mat. 4.23.\x*.
\s UJesu usilisa umlephero
\p
\v 40 Kwasekufika kuye umlephero, emncenga\x + Mat. 8.2-4. Luka 5.12-14.\x* eguqa ngamadolo phambi kwakhe\x + Mat. 17.14.\x*, esithi kuye: Aluba uthanda, ungangihlambulula.
\v 41 UJesu wasesiba lesihelo, welula isandla, wamthinta, wathi kuye: Ngiyathanda, hlambuluka;
\v 42 esekhulumile bahle basuka ubulephero kuye, wahlanjululwa.
\v 43 Wasemlayisisa\x + Mat. 9.30.\x*, wahle wamyekela wahamba,
\v 44 esithi kuye: Khangela ungatsheli muntu ulutho; kodwa hamba, uziveze kumpristi, unikele ngokuhlanjululwa kwakho lokho uMozisi akulayayo, kube yibufakazi kubo\x + 1.12.\x*.
\v 45 Kodwa yena esephumile waqala ukumemezela kakhulu\x + Luka 5.15.\x* walwandisa udaba\x + Mat. 9.31; 28.15.\x*, kwaze kwathi wayengaselakho ukungena emzini obala, kodwa wayengaphandle ezindaweni ezizinkangala\x + Luka 5.17.\x*; beza kuye bevela enhlangothini zonke\x + Mat. 4.25. Mark. 2.2,13; 3.7. Joha. 6.2.\x*.
